{"title":"妻","authors":["庄雪轩"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻有一副倾斜的肩膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是她负荷苦难的创伤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻的身腰已不苗条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一根粗短的树干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却那样坚实可靠；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柔和的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我家一对明亮的南窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么你对她的农村装束，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投射奇异的目光？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我却爱她这样打扮着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同行在熙攘的街坊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我珍视她额上的皱纹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一篇同甘共苦的经历，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该写在脸上最显明的地方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄雪轩"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}